---
// FAQ section component
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-950">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl">
        Frequently asked questions
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-400">
        Everything you need to know about Jace
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <div class="card">
          <button class="w-full text-left flex items-center justify-between group" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <h3 class="heading-3">Is my email data secure?</h3>
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="mt-4 text-gray-300 hidden">
            Yes, absolutely. We use bank-level encryption to protect your data. Jace is CASA Tier 3 certified, 
            which means we meet the highest standards for security and privacy. Your emails are never shared 
            with third parties, and you can delete your data at any time.
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <div class="card">
          <button class="w-full text-left flex items-center justify-between group" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <h3 class="heading-3">Can I control how Jace drafts?</h3>
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="mt-4 text-gray-300 hidden">
            Yes! Jace learns from your writing style and preferences. You can set custom instructions, 
            adjust the tone and formality level, and even create templates for different types of emails. 
            The more you use Jace, the better it becomes at matching your unique voice.
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <div class="card">
          <button class="w-full text-left flex items-center justify-between group" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <h3 class="heading-3">Can Jace integrate with my existing email client?</h3>
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="mt-4 text-gray-300 hidden">
            Jace works seamlessly with Gmail, Outlook, and most major email providers. You can use it 
            through our web app, browser extension, or mobile app. Installation takes less than a minute, 
            and you don't need to change your existing email setup.
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ 4 -->
        <div class="card">
          <button class="w-full text-left flex items-center justify-between group" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <h3 class="heading-3">What if I need help or have more questions?</h3>
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="mt-4 text-gray-300 hidden">
            We're here to help! Plus plan users get priority support, and Pro users get 24/7 dedicated support. 
            You can reach us through email, chat, or our Discord community. We also have extensive documentation 
            and video tutorials to help you get the most out of Jace.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Still have a question in mind? 
          <a href="mailto:support@jace.ai" class="text-yellow-400 hover:text-yellow-300 font-medium">
            Contact us
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  function toggleFAQ(button) {
    const content = button.nextElementSibling;
    const arrow = button.querySelector('svg');
    
    if (content.classList.contains('hidden')) {
      content.classList.remove('hidden');
      arrow.classList.add('rotate-180');
    } else {
      content.classList.add('hidden');
      arrow.classList.remove('rotate-180');
    }
  }
</script>